WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.068 --> 00:00:05.571
<i> Well, it happened again...</i>

00:00:05.604 --> 00:00:07.407
<i> ...another tragedy.</i>

00:00:07.440 --> 00:00:08.674
<i> Will we ever learn?</i>

00:00:08.707 --> 00:00:10.176
<i> On a day like today,</i>

00:00:10.209 --> 00:00:12.712
<i> it's pointless to even post
 on social media.</i>

00:00:12.745 --> 00:00:14.147
<i> But I absolutely must.</i>

00:00:14.180 --> 00:00:15.982
<i> I can't, and I won't,</i>

00:00:16.015 --> 00:00:18.951
<i> and I cannot,
 and I will not stay silent.</i>

00:00:18.984 --> 00:00:20.720
<i> As an American...</i>

00:00:20.753 --> 00:00:21.854
<i> As an amateur stand-up</i> 
<i> comedian...</i>

00:00:21.887 --> 00:00:23.156
<i> As a privileged person</i>

00:00:23.189 --> 00:00:25.291
<i> who recognizes
 my own privilege...</i>

00:00:25.324 --> 00:00:27.126
<i> ...it is my duty
 to speak out.</i>

00:00:27.159 --> 00:00:28.761
<i> Admit it,
 you're all just posting</i>

00:00:28.794 --> 00:00:30.596
<i> on social media
 for the attention.</i>

00:00:30.629 --> 00:00:33.566
<i> Today is not about me.</i>

00:00:33.599 --> 00:00:35.268
<i> Share my post if you agree.</i>

00:00:35.301 --> 00:00:37.336
[Sobbing]

00:00:37.369 --> 00:00:42.275
♪♪

00:00:42.308 --> 00:00:44.410
<i> Today has
 deeply affected me</i>

00:00:44.443 --> 00:00:46.045
<i> on a personal level.</i>

00:00:46.078 --> 00:00:48.147
<i> My thoughts and prayers
 are with the victims</i>

00:00:48.180 --> 00:00:50.249
<i> of this horrendous tragedy.</i>

00:00:50.282 --> 00:00:53.986
<i> We have to fight fire
 with peace fire.</i>

00:00:54.019 --> 00:00:55.488
<i> Share my post if you agree.</i>

00:00:55.521 --> 00:00:56.923
<i> Just watch.</i>

00:00:56.956 --> 00:00:58.858
<i> Tomorrow, you'll go back
 to posting selfies</i>

00:00:58.891 --> 00:01:01.360
<i> and forget this tragedy
 ever happened.</i>

00:01:01.393 --> 00:01:03.329
♪♪

00:01:03.362 --> 00:01:04.831
[Both sigh]

00:01:04.864 --> 00:01:06.499
Feels good
to say something.

00:01:06.532 --> 00:01:07.734
It really does.

